          description:
            'The fundamental right of individuals to control their own lives, property, and decisions without state interference.',
        },
        {
          title: 'Voluntary Cooperation',
          description:
            'How free people can achieve more through voluntary exchange and cooperation than through state coercion.',
        },
        {
          title: 'Digital Freedom',
          description:
            'The importance of maintaining individual autonomy in digital spaces and resisting surveillance capitalism.',
        },
        {
          title: 'Market Processes',
          description:
            'Understanding how prices, competition, and entrepreneurship create wealth and solve problems without central planning.',
